发射能力”，美方才最终批准向中国出口900吨用于生产塑料的石墨，据说关键理由是“中国其实已获得了石墨加工技术和设备，即便美国不卖给中国，中国也可以从其他国家，例如从法国轻易获得。” 让美国人想不到的是，才过去了18年，如今中国已经是世界上最大的石墨生产国和出口国，美国还不得不反过来从中国进口各种石墨制品。例如在新能源汽车领域，中国提供了全球97%的石墨电极，美国新能源汽车企业承认完全依赖于中国制造的石墨电极。 这也从另一个角度说明了美国制造业的急剧衰退——但不管从哪个角度说，如今的尴尬处境，都是美国自己选择的道路…"},"attached_info":"CkEIn5H1nqHP9vtNEAMaCTExMjE5ODA0NyC8vcm6BjAAONMCQA1yCjYxMDU5NTg0NzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"47 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-48deb4237afd9afae6b433a17aeecc95_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1734010296.578133","card_id":"Q_5074836314","target":{"id":5074836314,"title":"对于一个理性的人，怎么提高自己的感性？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5074836314","type":"question","created":1732506444,"answer_count":42,"follower_count":59,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,10491,120345],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIn5H1nqHP9vtNEAMaCTExMTk5MTYxOCDM5o+6BjAAODtADnIKNTA3NDgzNjMxNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"45 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e264eadededb5a689129f5684b0218a2_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1734010296.578609","card_id":"Q_6460180072","target":{"id":6460180072,"title":"TikTok 提交紧急动议以阻止「不卖就禁」法案，下一步将何去何从？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6460180072","type":"question","created":1733801838,"answer_count":40,"follower_count":81,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[472,21438,140490,209209,550111],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"12月10日，TikTok在官方账号发布声明称，已提交一项紧急动议，以阻止TikTok禁令于明年1月19日生效。此前，美国哥伦比亚特区联邦巡回上诉法院维持一项